ーを育成。離職率改善・心理的安全性向上・自走型チームづくりを支援。日英バイリンガルでの研修も対応可。ぜひお問合せを！", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shinobuseto/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALFaGkBqIANA_H76a0MV2bVrCDb5gPoNPI", "recommendations/1/context": "Rubel managed Lianne directly", "recommendations/1/date": "May 31, 2009", "recommendations/1/description": "I had Lianne under my supervision for 9 months, first as Sales Manager; then as Senior Sales Manager. During this period, I have seen lots of energy, motivation and dedication to her work. She is a great PR and an Ambassador to Sofitel thanks to her amazing capacity to develop relationship with others; peers, clients and other business partners. Her great ability to work in an international environment was a plus. I will highly recommend her to any colleague in hotel industry as she is be a strong asset to the team she will belong to.", "recommendations/1/name": "Lianne Grootings Ritzen", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Hospitality & Guest Experience Consultant", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lianne-grootings-ritzen-4a855612/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKSnEABGvKQRDcnuTMIHS8_-I0L2yfkMvw", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Coralie worked with Rubel but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "October 6, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Working with Rubel has been very gratifying. He is a pro-active person and a hard-worker. Before and during the Olympic Games, he tried his best to answer to our VIP clients' requests and needs. His flexible working style and his ability to adapt were highly appreciated during such a challenging event.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Coralie Latchoumane", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Professeure des écoles", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/coralielatchoumane/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEw6LoBUXFaHXJkmIxrZKcZpiIs01iByOk", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Cynthia managed Rubel directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "June 24, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Rubel is an examplary Manager, able to command the trust and respect of his clients, subordinates and superiors. He examplifies professionalism and is diligent in his work. He manages and develop his team well and able to instil trust and confidence in the Management, highly responsible and committed to his work. Highly recommended as Executive Management of a hotel.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Cynthia Lim", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "DOSM at Intercontinental Shenzhen", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cynthia-lim-00369613/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALFOYMBoAENyK7YXYMMB_GQvcg-rSGjRgk", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Guy was Rubel's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "June 8, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Rubel  was hired as Director of Sales i/c Mice and  Special Projects in Jan 2008 at the Sofitel Wanda Beijing. His primary assignement was to handle the top corporate Olympic service providers (accounts) before and during the Olympics Games. Rubel has exceeded my expectations and both Jet Set Sports, Sportsworld or Aristea just to name a few and their high profile clients staying at the hotel have expressed their outmost satisfaction. \nInSept 08, Rubel was given additional responsabilities acting as ADOSM and he is as of June 09 , the new DOSM of the Sofitel Plaza Saigon. Needless to say that this promotion is the true reflection of his commitment and abilities.\nI wish Rubel all the very best in his new endeavours.\nGuy Poujoulat", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Guy Poujoulat", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/guy-poujoulat-39034a11/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJdPZwB17F80k9qkPXfRtrTmcyop-sGwyw", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Lianne reported directly to Rubel", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "May 26, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Rubel is professional, efficient, sociable and offers the best quality service even in adhoc situations. Allthough he has a lot of job responsabilities, he always makes quality time for questions or problems his staff meets during the day. Rubel is a pleasure to work for and if the opportunity is there, I'd love to work for him again.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Lianne Grootings Ritzen", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Hospitality & Guest Experience Consultant", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lianne-grootings-ritzen-4a855612/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKSnEABGvKQRDcnuTMIHS8_-I0L2yfkMvw", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Remco worked with Rubel but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "May 24, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Very talented, excellent trainer and always focus on being the best. Rubel's great character combined with his management skills and charisma has earned him not only awards but the respect he deserves.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Remco Louwerse", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Revenue Manager bij Center Parcs", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/remcolouwerse/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEz1w0BWCQuDZ0ugoaK_wIi4Y6QUOSZ_pE", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Anne managed Rubel directly", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "May 21, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "During the period working with Rubel, I was acting as DoSM on Mission for Sofitel Wanda Beijing. I found Rubel extremely efficient, proactive, organised, and loyal.  He is dedicated to his work and has a passion for it.  He handles situations well and is also willing to take advice and learn.  Extremely dependable and a hard worker, he always finds solutions to difficult challenges. I wish him success in all his future endeavours. \n\nAnne S Lewinski \nDirector Sales and Marketing on Mission\nSofitel Wanda Beijing\nFeb to May 2009", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Anne Lewinski", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Sales & Marketing Hospitality Consultant:", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/aslewinski/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAATvywBLUATlXgaDzoAmofoejudhHFzEFY", "skills/0/title": "Contract Negotiation", "skills/1/title": "Business Development", "skills/2/title": "Customer Loyalty", "skills/3/title": "Customer Service", "skills/4/title": "Food and Beverage Operations", "skills/5/title": "Employee Relations", "skills/6/title": "Team Leadership", "skills/7/title": "Sales and Marketing", "skills/8/title": "Marketing", "skills/9/title": "Business Planning", "skills/10/title": "Centricity", "skills/11/title": "Operations Management", "skills/12/title": "Coaching & Mentoring", "skills/13/title": "Business Acumen", "skills/14/title": "Revenue & Profit Growth", "skills/15/title": "Project Management", "skills/16/title": "Building Strong Teams", "skills/17/title": "Revenue driven", "skills/18/title": "Business Strategy", "skills/19/title": "Hotels", "totalExperienceYears": "21.8", "totalRecommendationsGiven": "2", "totalRecommendationsReceived": "6", "urn": "ACoAAAFHtw4BlDMsn44zcX6Ef85SzH4wxLnC_PY", "volunteerAndAwards/0/description": "Working with all Marriott International hotels in Greater Bangkok to raise awareness and funds for Operations Foundation in Thailand primarily working on educating on the occurrence of cleft lips and palates worldwide and operating on young children affected by cleft lips and palate malformation threatening their daily life and affecting their social life.", "volunteerAndAwards/0/duration/months": "0", "volunteerAndAwards/0/duration/years": "0", 